Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:32.79,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.79,0:24:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Beer bottle caps!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:39.99,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
