Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.17,0:24:37.57,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The culprit vanished like bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.57,0:24:38.60,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:39.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Whoa, whoa, whoa...
